Gate (Erc20 DAI Address) (Erc20 Deploy Standard DAI "Dai")
Gate (Erc20 REP Address) (Erc20 Deploy Standard REP "Augur")
Gate (Erc20 USDC Address) (Erc20 Deploy Standard USDC "USD Coin" 6)

-- Now deploy our cTokens
Gate (GToken gZRX Address) (GToken Deploy CErc20 gZRX "Test 0x ðŸ“ˆ" (Erc20 ZRX Address) (Comptroller Address) (InterestRateModel InterestRateModel Address) 0.2e9 8)
Gate (GToken gBAT Address) (GToken Deploy CErc20 gBAT "Test Basic Attention Token ðŸ“ˆ" (Erc20 BAT Address) (Comptroller Address) (InterestRateModel InterestRateModel Address) 0.2e9 8)
Gate (GToken gDAI Address) (GToken Deploy CErc20 gDAI "Test Dai ðŸ“ˆ" (Erc20 DAI Address) (Comptroller Address) (InterestRateModel InterestRateModel Address) 0.2e9 8)
Gate (GToken gREP Address) (GToken Deploy CErc20 gREP "Test Augur ðŸ“ˆ" (Erc20 REP Address) (Comptroller Address) (InterestRateModel InterestRateModel Address) 0.2e9 8)
Gate (GToken gETH Address) (GToken Deploy CEther gETH "Test Ether ðŸ“ˆ" (Comptroller Address) (InterestRateModel InterestRateModel Address) 0.2e9 8)
Gate (GToken gUSDC Address) (GToken Deploy CErc20 gUSDC "Test USD Coin ðŸ“ˆ" (Erc20 USDC Address) (Comptroller Address) (InterestRateModel InterestRateModel Address) 2e-4 8)

